  "title": "Lousy Parents",
  "description": "In this brand-new comedy by Trevor Schmidt, Carly from Sunshine Daycare Home has the unenviable task of informing her charges’ parents of a lice outbreak in the daycare. Tensions rise, blame is placed, and comedy ensues. Join the festival’s favourite lawyer-actors for their 10th year! All proceeds benefit the Varscona Theatre.",
